title: Tier 5 Honor Ward
body: I am currently a Tier 5 Honor and I see people with those sick Honor wards and I was just wondering when Riot plans to distribute them. I realize the team has to sort between who gets what rewards just wanted to see what the latency would be.

replies.body: Not all of the ranked/honor rewards have been sent out just yet. They'll still be going out over the course of Nov, but if you still don't see yours in about a week reach out to us in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
